data.title: FBI Busca A Juan José Esparragoza Moreno El Azul (Inglés)
data.meta_description: FBI Busca a Juan José Esparragoza Moreno «El Azul» (Inglés) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Juan Jose Esparragoza-Moreno is wanted for conspiracy to import and distribute controlled substances and importation of a controlled substance. A $5 million reward is offered for information leading to his arrest. He is believed to have undergone plastic surgery and to lead a drug trafficking organization responsible for importing over 14 tons of marijuana into the United States. He should be considered armed and dangerous.
